Ok, if WindLord is way off, I guess Scrat is back with the others.

::Scrat::

Scrat watches the Deemos situation from the shadows, trembling in 
fright. He sees Trinity attack Deemos, and sees Deemos aiming the 
blaster at Trinity.

"Watch out!" he yells, and, fighting his fear, jumps out from the 
trees, trying to tackle Trinity out of the way.
